import React from "react";
import { Modal, Row, Col, Form as FormBS } from "react-bootstrap";

import Button from "../button/Button";

const Form = () => {
	return (
		<Modal show={true} size="lg">
			<Modal.Header closeButton>
				<Modal.Title>Agrega un personaje</Modal.Title>
			</Modal.Header>
			<Modal.Body>
				<FormBS>
					<Row>
						<Col sm={6}>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Nombre</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Control type="text" />
								<FormBS.Text className="text-muted">
									We'll never share your email with anyone else.
								</FormBS.Text>
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
						<Col sm={6}>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Cumpleaños</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Control type="date" />
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
						<Col>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Color de Ojos</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Control type="text" />
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
						<Col>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Color de Pelo</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Control type="text" />
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
						<Col>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Género</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Check inline label="Mujer" name="genero" type="radio" />
								<FormBS.Check inline label="Hombre" name="genero" type="radio" />
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
						<Col>
							<FormBS.Group controlId="">
								<FormBS.Label>Posicióm</FormBS.Label>
								<FormBS.Check
									inline
									label="Estudiante"
									name="estudiante"
									type="radio"
								/>
								<FormBS.Check
									inline
									label="Staff"
									name="estudiante"
									type="radio"
								/>
							</FormBS.Group>
						</Col>
					</Row>
					<Button>Guardar</Button>
				</FormBS>
			</Modal.Body>
		</Modal>
	);
};

export default Form;
